    dc:title "A new species of Chrysobothris Eschscholtz feeding on Dudleya spp. (Crassulaceae) from California and Baja California, with biological, distributional and taxonomic notes on other North American Buprestidae (Coleoptera)" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.179395>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.179397>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.179396>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.179398> ;
