<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.179395>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 6. Chrysobothris dudleyaphaga, sp. nov.: Figs. 1 – 2, adult dorsal habitus, 1, female and 2, male, from San Diego Co., California; Fig. 3, aedeagus from type locality; Fig. 4, larva from Dudleya edulis, San Diego Co.; Fig. 5, pupal cells from Dudleya edulis; Fig. 6, adult exit hole in Dudleya ingens." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/179395/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.179397>
    dc:description "FIGURES 8 – 9. Adults at type locality, July 1988: Fig. 8, adult on host, Dudleya ingens; Fig. 9, adult feeding on same host." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/179397/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.179396>
    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Type locality, general aspect of habitat, July 1988." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/179396/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.179398>
    dc:description "FIGURES 10 – 11. Otay Mesa & Heritage Roads, San Diego Co., California, July 1988: Fig. 10, general aspect of habitat; Fig. 11, host, Dudleya edulis." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/179398/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

